imdb.plot outline: "Timor Live - Art in a New Country" - The new country of East Timor has already endured a great deal of suffering, but in spite of all the turmoil, the creative spirit lives on. Through this Season "Timor Live" meet several of East Timor's artists and see how Timor's musicians, both new and experienced are using their creative talents to inspire their nation and help bring it forward.
